text: Amblymora instabilis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pascoe in 1867. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Amblymora instabilis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1867
title: Amblymora instabilis
